title: The Enchanted Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Coffee house cafe offering a casual food menu, free Wi-Fi, and is frequented by students. Veg include a hummus & veggie sandwich, a black bean quinoa burger, a vegan hummus sandwich, and customize your own salad. Has plant milk for drinks. Hosts psychic readings, dancing nights, and events.
